      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is in absolute showroom condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot. Not a scratch on it! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the typical dealership headache, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
