    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The VANOS system has been professionally overhauled with Beisan components, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis is structurally perfect, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common fatigue points. It sits on a corner-balanced Bilstein PSS10 coilover setup, maintaining optimal roll centers while sharpening turn-in response. The Laguna Seca Blue finish remains factory-spec with no evidence of panel respray or oxidation. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
