    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating and absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of compression or wear, the dashboard is free of any UV damage, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade piece for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Complete with two sets of keys, original window sticker, and a clean title in hand.",
